### ============================================
### 1. CHECK AVAILABILITY - Public (No Auth Required)
### ============================================
### This checks which tables are free for a specific date/time
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/availability?date=2024-12-25&timeSlot=18:00&numberOfGuests=4
Content-Type: application/json

### Expected Response: 200 OK
### Returns: Array of available tables that can fit 4 guests
### Note: Only shows tables with capacity >= numberOfGuests and status = "active"


### ============================================
### 2. CHECK AVAILABILITY - Different Time Slot
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/availability?date=2024-12-25&timeSlot=19:00&numberOfGuests=2
Content-Type: application/json

### Expected Response: 200 OK
### Returns: More tables available (capacity >= 2)


### ============================================
### 3. CHECK AVAILABILITY - Large Party
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/availability?date=2024-12-25&timeSlot=20:00&numberOfGuests=8
Content-Type: application/json

### Expected Response: 200 OK
### Returns: Only tables with capacity >= 8


