### 5. CREATE RESERVATION - Customer (Success)
### ============================================
### IMPORTANT: Login as customer first and copy token above
### Also copy a tableId from the availability check
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "table": "{{tableId}}",
  "date": "2024-12-25",
  "timeSlot": "18:00",
  "numberOfGuests": 4,
  "contactPhone": "1234567890",
  "specialRequests": "Window seat preferred"
}

### Expected Response: 201 Created
### Returns: Created reservation with status "pending"
### Copy the _id and update @reservationId variable above


